        "sender_full_name": "Ben Nale",
        "timestamp": 1597100912
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>you can use <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib_docs/tactics.html#conv\">tactic#conv</a> to focus in on the part of the goal you want to rewrite.</p>",
        "id": 206524013,
        "sender_full_name": "Alex J. Best",
        "timestamp": 1597101049
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib_docs/tactics.html#nth_rewrite%20/%20nth_rewrite_lhs%20/%20nth_rewrite_rhs\">nth_rewrite</a> is relevant, too, I think</p>",
